Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========Pre=========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.48,0:00:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========OP=========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:36.79,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:46.28,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}僕らの願いが届くまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:55.09,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}大事なものまた一つ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:00:59.74,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}モノクロの空へと消える
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:06.62,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隠したキズ冷たく震え
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.55,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分の居場所を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:18.82,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}常識に従うこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:23.34,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}どうしようもできないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:27.59,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}壊していきたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:35.21,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}閉ざしたココロ叫んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:42.57,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:48.27,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分さえも見失いそうになって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:52.52,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}曖昧な答えはイラナイ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:58.77,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}確かな今　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:36.79,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲伤的连锁之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:46.28,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在我们的愿望实现之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:55.09,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}又一件珍贵的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:00:59.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}消失在黑白的空中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:06.62,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隐藏的伤痕在发冷颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去找寻我的容身之处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:18.82,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在这个遵循常识的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:23.34,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想打破无可救药的桎梏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:27.59,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}按自己的意志自由生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:35.21,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}封闭的心灵正发出呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:42.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲伤的连锁之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:48.27,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我们几乎快要迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:52.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不需要暧昧的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:58.77,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}只需去追寻真切的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======TEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏第七小队护送我平安返回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.01,0:02:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时在城中休息 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就此告退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金先生 这也是艾丽西娅的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请理解她的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问这样就满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 罗茜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 艾丽西娅的离开我们每个人都有责任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在却在这里受艾丽西娅的保护
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她此时此刻也在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊 被对方的女武神压制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹豫什么 吉兰达约近在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何应对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是怪物 遇上同类就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军 第三第五坦克中队失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么 快把部队撤到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全…到底哪里是安全所在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在为什么而战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没有了归宿 没有要保护的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量只有这种程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么忘我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…很早以前就认识她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识的艾丽西娅·梅尔姬沃特已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 即便如此我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了 当时的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么这么忘我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是那里出身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫艾丽西娅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪听起来耳熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你也在那间收容所呆过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在老交情上劝你一句
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗时不要带有多余的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是敌人的计谋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则为什么会在这时…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千真万确
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国军加利亚方面军总司令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安·盖伦斯本·雷金莱布亲自前来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求缔结停战协议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向来是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑电波与Ragnite反应值都超过基准值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等级28 优秀的数值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他候选者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想办法遣散 这里对外的形象是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向孤儿伸出援手的慈善设施
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A1号的转移手续拜托了 尽快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑几次才肯罢休 只有这里会收留你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来A1号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗A1号 只要你还是女武神的后裔实验就会继续
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家彼此之间该如何相处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该懂点事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不识好歹 随你便吧 但你的未来不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨过这个世界 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 A1号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅一次邂逅改变了我的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A1号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛尔贝莉亚 是这种花的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后就是你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效力于吾 伴随吾身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛尔贝莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把敌人的主力全部交给赛尔贝莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将去和加利亚说悄悄话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是佯动作战 没想到能如此轻易接近兰蒂格瑞丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人也顾不过来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有抵抗结果也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你担心也没用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结这份协议绝不会让你们后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你口中的停战到底是何含义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如字面上的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:12:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为结束这场令百姓受苦\N并可能毁灭加利亚一切的消耗战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战局正倾向我方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续打下去的话我们将赢得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们为何在此交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么选择这个时间点上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亚的国民们确实饱受这场战争的煎熬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并非我本愿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说出你的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰蒂格瑞丝城的无血开城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科迪莉亚 成为吾的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便缔结政治婚姻也不可能让民众忘记这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事自不用说 多此一言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是继承加利亚的王位 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这种事 发起这场战争？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你称其为“这种事”？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何其迂腐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要拥有王位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要拥有兰蒂格瑞丝王族中 女武神的血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就意味着拥有了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用身陷帝国的权力斗争中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够建立起吾心目中的国度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是女武神族的后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 达鲁库斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 我一直在考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望什么 怎么样才能为你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 今后要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 背着这么大包行李
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都猜得出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗茜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷跑可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉鲁高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打算去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也别想甩下我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做的话 你们也会上军事法庭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 我们已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我必须去向艾丽西娅道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这样下去绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都想通了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅是不是女武神人没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:14:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 今后我会按自己的意愿行动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在…想见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她拥有 但是我却没有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量？不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有要守护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一种觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的战斗理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有输不起的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这种力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 接下来的一击中分出胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等什么 杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有要保护的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能那样坚强地战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你让我想起自己也有宝贵的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太心软了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然输给这种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要活着就有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金这么说过 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你还不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败给你的瞬间 我已经没有任何价值
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着 肯定还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:18:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒为女武神人后 还能说出这种理想主义论调
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈话到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 擒住她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要贯彻我的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛尔贝莉亚 你要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在我心目中重于一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 没有死亡成就的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达鲁库斯人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要公布自己是达鲁库斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰蒂格瑞丝家族的威信将归入尘土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也无法再利用我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这虚假的历史 到了该结束的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们已无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下来电
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:19:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 去完成其他目的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:21:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和吉兰达约以及赛尔贝莉亚上校失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 赛尔贝莉亚还有用她的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校对您那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为您而战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挡住吾去路的人 只此一种下场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======ED=======
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:47.31,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}悲しすぎる瞳が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:53.98,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}この空を映す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:22:02.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}掛ける言葉がわからずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:08.22,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただ　星を数えた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:13.94,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤独で居る世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:20.72,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}得意なはずだと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:27.23,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}振りかえる日々　あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:33.66,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}探していた　きみをひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:40.30,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}もしもいま許されるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:46.99,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}きみのことだけ想うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:54.88,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}忘れたくない悲しみならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.34,0:23:02.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただそれが　それだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:08.62,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\be1}そう  ひとつの願い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:47.31,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}太过悲伤的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:53.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}映照出这片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:22:02.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}不知该说什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:08.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只默默数着星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:13.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤独的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:20.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}早该习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:27.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}回首往日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:33.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我曾独自将你找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:40.30,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}若此刻能得到允许
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:46.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我愿心中只思念着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:54.88,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}若不愿忘却这悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.34,0:23:02.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}仅此而已 唯有此心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:08.62,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\be1}是的 那是唯一的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======NEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人无法一个人生存
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果只会伤害别人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着究竟有何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.76,0:23:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有恐怖力量为加利亚而战之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 战场女武神 第二十五章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须保护的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.37,0:23:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也算为保护大家…出过一份力了
